This paper discusses the need for powerful query management capabilities in data management systems, which is a topic closely related to database management (cs.DB) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The paper also mentions the challenges associated with building such a system, which could fall under the categories of deep learning (cs.DL), human-computer interaction (cs.HC), and social and information networks (cs.SI).
